---
// Hero — the single most important section. Edit copy directly here.
// The <em> tag receives the accent color + italic treatment.
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>I build the infrastructure that earns the right to feel <em>boring</em>.</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    At Elastic I direct the ingest portfolio behind OpenTelemetry, Elastic Agent, and
    APM Server — the layer that decides whether petabyte-scale systems feel steady or
    chaotic. After hours, I maintain FastMCP and the agent infrastructure that only
    gets hard once real traffic and real failure modes show up.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-row">
    <a href="/writing" class="primary">Read the writing</a>
    <a href="/projects" class="secondary">Open source</a>
    <a href="/about" class="secondary">More about me</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 40px 0 80px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 88px);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  .hero h1 :global(em) {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  .hero .lede {
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 26px;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .hero .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .hero .cta-row a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 44px;
    padding: 0 16px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease;
  }
  .hero .cta-row a:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }
  .hero .cta-row .primary {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
  }
  .hero .cta-row .secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    color: var(--ink);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, white 30%, var(--bg) 70%);
  }
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .hero .lede {
      font-size: 19px;
    }
  }
</style>
